Internationalization : 12/04/2021
    Local Class     :
    Properties      :


Introduction :
    * Problem of customizing a program or page for different countries or languages
    * It would be highly problematic to create and maintain enough different versions to meet the needs of all clients
      everywhere.

Internationalization :
    * It is a process of designing an application so that it can be adapted to various regions and languages without
      engineering changes.
    * Java is first language to support internationalization.
    * i18n : abbreviation for internationalization.

    Characterisation :
        * with the addition od localised data, the same executable can run worldwide.


